偏藍，利益行先<br />\n<br />\nLa prairie view&nbsp;<br />\n2809 0100(公司投訴部)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.laprairie.com.hk/en_HK/contact-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.laprairie.com.hk%2Fen_HK%2Fcontact-us&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4ey4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=10237605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.laprairie.com.hk/en_HK/contact-us</a><br />\n*警嫂* Yuki Wong (Festival Walk)<br />\n☎3105 0855<br />\n話示威者顛倒黑白<br />\n<br />\n*警嫂* Zoe (沙田新城市)&nbsp;<br />\n☎2487 7011<br />\n長期打仔人啲仔女fans<br />\n<br />\n*警嫂* Cola Chan (尖沙咀k11 muse) <br />\n☎9170 0736/2771 8816<br />\n長期叫人曱甴<br />\n<br />\nCharlene (中環IFC)<br />\n☎6298 4204/2524 6136<br />\n長期唔收工要獨市<br />\n<br />\nLanc&ocirc;me<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lancome.com.hk/en_HK/contact?dwcont=C1849138882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lancome.com.hk%2Fen_HK%2Fcontact%3Fdwcont%3DC1849138882&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4ey4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=df0e748a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lancome.com.hk/en_HK/contact?dwcont=C1849138882</a><br />\nBarbara Woo (元朗Yoho mall）<br />\n<br />\nLaneige<br />\n*警嫂* Kiko Ng (Times Square)<br />\n成日話曱甴令佢無生意<br />\n<br />\nMAC<br />\nNicole Yuen (元朗Yoho)<br />\n朋友做曱甴 經常鬧示威者抵死 深藍<br />\n<br />\nMana Beauty<br />\nEva Lo (旺角T.O.P Mall)<br />\n腦殘深藍<br />\n<br />\nVINE VERA<br />\nMAGGIE CHEUNG (lab n facesss)<br />\n☎96127785<br />\n扮黃得很嚴重，對人講人話對鬼講鬼話！仲有篤灰，令到一位黃絲同事，俾上頭話唔好番工講政治！<br />\n<br />\nYSL<br />\n*警嫂* Chili Lam (CWB sogo counter manager)<br />\n☎6093&nbsp;5385<br />\n佢老公係差人&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n*警嫂* Seayato Yue (CWB sogo YSL beauty advisor )<br />\n☎6159 4805&nbsp;<br />\n男朋友係黑警前線扑尻手足<br />\n<br />\n*警嫂* Mandy (尖沙咀 Lane Crawford Assistant counter manager)<br />\n☎60189995<br />\n老公係警察，成日話自己中立撚<br />\n<br />\n*警嫂* Vicky (尖沙咀 Lane Crawford)<br />\n☎67043002<br />\n男朋友係防暴<br />\n<br />\n*警嫂* Crystal (尖沙咀 Lane Crawford)<br />\n☎55067780<br />\n同返個前男友（警察）一齊<br />\n<br />\nShirley&nbsp; (尖沙咀 Lane Crawford收銀)<br />